comments: Great class, great subject, learned a lot. Lots of free food samples. Pay attention in class, study well and you\'ll make it.
if you come to class and pay attention, this is an easy grade

Easy and helpful. If you need any help just ask him. If you go to class every day and pay attention you will do well. For the nutrition class I took he offered at least 4 pt. extra credit every day. Has a accent, but its not that bad.
